copy.title: Pinecone Pop
copy.retryMessage: Aw, sugar, you ran out of Pinecones! But you still have some chances left. How about you try this level again?
copy.tutorial_finalscore_label: Now let's crack that ice and free those flower bulbs!
copy.interactive_bubble_emptyBulb: Aim for the PINK ice, sugar.
copy.interactive_bubble_wait: Aim at the PINK ice, and THROW a pinecone to crack it!
copy.interactive_bubble_gameOver: Try again, sugar! Aim for the PINK ice.
copy.tutorial_txt_01: Welcome to Snowcap Glade, sugar! We need to free the flower bulbs trapped in the ice so we can take them to the mainland for spring!
copy.tutorial_txt_02: Toss a pinecone at the pink ice to crack it and free the flower bulbs inside.
copy.tutorial_txt_03: Easy, see? And don't fret if you hit the blue ice -- there aren't any flower bulbs inside those.
copy.tutorial_txt_03b: Always try to aim at the PINK ice, got it?
copy.tutorial_txt_04: Flaptastic pinecone tossing! Try to hit all the ice you can with each toss. You don't have a lot of pinecones, so you might run out if you're not careful!
copy.tutorial_txt_05: This thingy here tells you how many pinecones you have left. Always check here before you throw.
copy.tutorial_txt_06: Sometimes if you're lucky, your pinecone will land in this basket here at the bottom. When that happens you get a FREE PINECONE. Like this, watch!
copy.tutorial_txt_07: Now you try again. Hit all the PINK ice!
copy.tutorial_txt_08: Good job, sugar! You can see your score over here.
copy.tutorial_txt_10: This tells you how many flower bulbs you still have to get free.
copy.tutorial_txt_11: That's all there is to it! Remember, I'll be here with you the whole time, okay?
copy.welcome_text: Hi there Fairy Friend! Welcome to Sunflower Meadow! I'm sorting seeds to plant in the spring. I get a little mixed up sometimes. Can you help me pick up pairs of seeds?
copy.easy_story: Ready to free some flower bulbs for spring? Then start tossing those pinecones!
copy.medium_story: You'll need to aim carefully, sugar. Get ready!
copy.hard_story: These flower bulbs will be a little tricky to get. Good luck!
copy.royal_story: It will take some fancy pinecone tossing to get these flower bulbs free. I know you can do it!
copy.easy_exitstory: You're pretty nifty with those pinecones, sugar. Thanks tons for the flaptastic job!
copy.medium_exitstory: You've been such a help, sugar. I really appreciate it!
copy.hard_exitstory: Look at that! You got tons of flower bulbs for spring! Plant-astic job, sugar!
copy.royal_exitstory: I am so impressed! I think you're the best pinecone pitcher I've ever seen!
copy.allmedium_story: You freed a lot of flower bulbs from the ice, but we still need more. Keep going!
copy.allhard_story: The next batch of flower bulbs are caught in some pretty thick ice. Aim carefully now!
copy.allroyal_story: We almost have enough flower bulbs for spring. Let's see if we can get the rest!
copy.level_tip_1: Remember to aim for PINK ice, got it? Only pink ice has flower bulbs inside.
copy.level_tip_2: Only hit blue ice when you need to get it out of the way. Rocks don't disappear, so toss around them.
copy.level_tip_3: If your pinecone lands in the basket, you get an extra pinecone.
copy.level_tip_5: Hit the red ice to earn 3 Hot Shots! That means the next 3 pinecones will melt right through any ice in their path!
copy.level_tip_7: Hit the green ice, and your pinecone will split into 3 pinecones! It's a triple-pinecone bonus!
copy.level_tip_10: Hit the yellow ice to earn Leaf Extensions for your basket. They'll let you catch more pinecones and flower bulbs!
copy.level_tip_12: Toss your pinecone into a Speed Chute to give it a boost. It will move faster and hit more ice drops!
copy.level_tip_15: Hit the purple ice to make Bumpers appear. They can bounce your pinecone back up for more pinecone popping!
copy.level_tip_20: If you hit the orange ice, you'll get an extra pinecone!
copy.game_over_win_1: You got all the flower bulbs for spring! Oh, sugar, you've made me a very happy garden-talent!
copy.game_over_win_2: You've done a flaptastic job, sugar! I give you a double-wing salute!
copy.game_over_win_3: Congratulations, sugar! Spring will be filled with flowers thanks to you!
copy.game_over_win_4: Wow, you're way better at this than I am! Spring will be brighter thanks to you!
copy.game_over_lose_0: Well, you gave it your best, right? You can always try again!
copy.game_over_lose_1: Oh well! I'm proud of you, sugar. You're welcome to try again any time!
copy.instruction0: Use your mouse to aim at the ice pegs, and then click the left mouse button to toss a pinecone. Try to break as much ice as you can on each throw!
copy.instruction1: You need to crack all the pink ice to clear a level!
copy.instruction2: If your pinecone lands in the basket at the bottom, you get an extra pinecone to toss again!
copy.instruction3: Power-ups make cracking ice easier! Aim for the different colored ice to get a power-up!
copy.instruction4: Use the chutes to propel your pinecone across the level, and into hard to reach places!
